From: sOkam <7308253+heysokam@users.noreply.github.com>
Subject: [PATCH] Demote missing sound and background music warnings to developer print

Demote missing sound and background music warnings to developer print

Files: code/client/snd_dma.c

Co-authored-by: eugene <eugene@832414e2-6573-9c40-a513-caa1f8131539>
---
diff --git a/code/client/snd_dma.c b/code/client/snd_dma.c
index 46f0c331..c56a834d 100644
--- a/code/client/snd_dma.c
+++ b/code/client/snd_dma.c
@@ -1292,7 +1292,7 @@ static void S_OpenBackgroundStream( const char *filename ) {
 	}
 
 	if( s_backgroundStream->info.channels != 2 || s_backgroundStream->info.rate != 22050 ) {
-		Com_Printf(S_COLOR_YELLOW "WARNING: music file %s is not 22k stereo\n", filename );
+		Com_DPrintf(S_COLOR_YELLOW "WARNING: music file %s is not 22k stereo\n", filename );
 	}
 }
 

-- 
